      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2019-07-25</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2020-09-25T13:25:55Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Eleanor Smith Inclusive Home Design Act of 2019</strong></p> <p>This bill requires certain newly constructed, federally assisted housing, including single-family homes and town houses, to contain at least one level that complies with specified minimum standards of accessibility for individuals with disabilities. An aggrieved person may commence a civil action with respect to a violation of this requirement.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
